---
import EventLayout from "../../components/EventLayout.astro";

const images = [
  { src: "/robotics-i/1.jpg", alt: "Robotics Hackathon I" },
  { src: "/robotics-i/2.JPG", alt: "Robotics Hackathon I" },
  { src: "/robotics-i/3.jpg", alt: "Robotics Hackathon I" },
  { src: "/robotics-i/4.jpg", alt: "Robotics Hackathon I" },
  { src: "/robotics-i/6.jpg", alt: "Robotics Hackathon I" },
];
---

<EventLayout
  title="Robotics Hackathon I"
  date="June 14-15, 2025"
  location="Antwerp, Belgium"
  type="Hackathon"
  description="North Star's first two-day hackathon and part of the worldwide LeRobot Hackathon - where a local team took home a global prize."
  images={images}
>
  <p>The first Robotics Hackathon was a milestone - our inaugural two-day event, and part of the worldwide LeRobot Hackathon. Over an intensive weekend, teams bridged the gap between digital intelligence and physical interaction.</p>
  <p>Team W.A.S.A.B.I. won the local competition and took home an AgileX Robotics PiPER research arm. Team smolmanager went further - securing the LeKiwi prize in the global competition. A local team, competing from Antwerp, winning a worldwide robotics hackathon.</p>
  <p>This is just the beginning of our robotics journey. More events covering embodied AI, hardware integration, and everything that bridges the digital and physical worlds are coming.</p>
</EventLayout>
